{"tid":1848472,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"「不主張各國撤僑」　WHO秘書長：對中國防疫能力有信心","createTime":"2020-01-28T13:07:36.000Z","updateTime":"2020-01-31T03:51:54.000Z","uid":141151,"like":0,"dislike":10,"uniUserReply":13,"replies":[{"pid":"233f20475d3c75f00d906ba497cdb9d5c6c08ed4","tid":1848472,"uid":141151,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-28T13:07:36.000Z","msg":"「不主張各國撤僑」　WHO秘書長：對中國防疫能力有信心<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.upmedia.mg/news_info.php?SerialNo=80250\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.upmedia.mg%2Fnews_info.php%3FSerialNo%3D80250&d=rcEdfnhTqGmqsB%2B6X%2FYCGSvt59O44HeJS3%2BtxtDyp5g%3D&h=e04ff4b6\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.upmedia.mg/news_info.php?SerialNo=80250</a><br />\n<br />\n中國武漢肺炎疫情延燒，世界衛生組織（WHO）秘書長譚德塞（Tedros Ghebreyesus）28日飛抵北京與中國外交部長王毅商談防疫問題，譚德塞指出，WHO不建議各國從武漢撤僑，並稱「對中國政府防疫能力充滿信心。」<br />\n <br />\n據中國媒體《澎湃》報導，譚德塞讚揚在武漢肺炎疫情爆發後，中國在創紀錄的短時間內分離出病株，向WHO及其他國家分享病毒的基因序列，並迅速採取一系列強而有效的防疫措施，令人深感敬佩。<br />\n <br />\n據報導，針對美國、法國及日韓等國陸續自武漢撤僑後，譚德塞表示世衛組織對中國政府防控疫情的能力充滿信心，也呼籲國際社會「不需過度反應」，並稱世衛組織不主張撤僑，「在當前形勢下應保持鎮定。」<br />\n <br />\n王毅則表示，對於WHO秉持公正客觀立場評價中國實施的防疫舉措，令人讚賞。中國也願繼續秉持著公開透明的態度，與國際社會及WHO加強合作，為國際公衛作出貢獻。"},{"pid":"e24d706241a1b2f90b10eeb3196549d552a7ee21","tid":1848472,"uid":345458,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-28T13:08:01.000Z","msg":"入去推10下！<br />\n<br />\n「正視聽！」拆解林鄭記招政策幾乎零作用！全力籌備1.29 2.03大三罷！<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1848456\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1848456</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區"},{"pid":"f8e7b974567fe171dba566daf1cc126f8736a656","tid":1848472,"uid":205482,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-28T13:10:42.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/lny/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n死性不改 1.29罷佢老母<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1848465\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1848465</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區"},{"pid":"cf46234be7dc29ea818610ce5837da4a592b6058","tid":1848472,"uid":86186,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-28T13:11:40.000Z","msg":"信你都on9"},{"pid":"2db67202a4f14946098f01f8254da76983c5f827","tid":1848472,"uid":179013,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-28T13:13:16.000Z","msg":"雪雪聲<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0b27e7eeac8600a979c930f16f034fc3e7b2f055","tid":1848472,"uid":40267,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-01-28T13:14:54.000Z","msg":"奶共其次<br />\n重點係who本來就廢物嚟<br />\nGoogle下幾年前伊波拉搞成點就知"},{"pid":"1b402ecb107d2a5e0f82ebeb3665b7260a8a1a36","tid":1848472,"uid":522,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-28T13:16:46.000Z","msg":"收左幾多錢"},{"pid":"1f2534ffa195b2570180e77be73d475b6100c21d","tid":1848472,"uid":60434,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"0b27e7eeac8600a979c930f16f034fc3e7b2f055","tid":1848472,"uid":40267,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-01-28T13:14:54.000Z","msg":"奶共其次<br />\n重點係who本來就廢物嚟<br />\nGoogle下幾年前伊波拉搞成點就知"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-28T13:19:26.000Z","msg":"伊波拉作用係清洗nigga，今次武漢肺炎一樣"},{"pid":"db25390f4a5dda729a8691de9d59577582ede9da","tid":1848472,"uid":114217,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-28T13:23:53.000Z","msg":"聯合國同世衛已經無人信架啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/lny/z.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5f6c93188bb3625ea21f2ddf8b141aa32e93e9ef","tid":1848472,"uid":293947,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-28T13:40:19.000Z","msg":"收咗錢講好話,你睇佢同習總講野系隔三張檯,平時的訪客唔會隔咁遠就知有幾嚴重.<img src=\"/assets/faces/lny/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b7d8308acf8201bfd93ca53ad7deb9692eae6fe1","tid":1848472,"uid":46120,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-28T13:48:35.000Z","msg":"如果佢講係因為擔心無發燒都可以感染，而且潛伏期極長，又擔心撤僑反而將疫情向全世界散開爆發，都會有人理解。<br />\n<br />\n不過佢話「對中國防疫能力有信心」，而且上星期先話唔需要理依個疫情，支那會攪得掂，哈哈哈。 <br />\n<br />\nWHO一早係支那控制住喇，文明國家自己成立一個世界衛生組織喇，要加埋台灣國同香港國。<br />\n<br />\n文明國家標準，最簡單係睇護照免簽數目。"},{"pid":"db1ad4e9caefe92b59d13815a589cefdd53dcd51","tid":1848472,"uid":19692,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-31T03:51:18.000Z","msg":"1346年 神聖羅馬帝國表示對控制黑死病疫情有信心<img src=\"/assets/faces/lny/devil.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7ee6d8533bbf04b34d69b0076b1ac52bb48e6010","tid":1848472,"uid":223643,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-31T03:51:54.000Z","msg":"【疫情展望】手足做好防護措施，去到 Phase II. 就仆街<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1850403\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1850403</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區"}]}